{"tid":199264,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"求救：IT界至荀工","createTime":"2017-04-13T05:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T08:13:39.000Z","uid":102722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7de57deb91027228be2c4b4e9a50f0ea1192a2b2","tid":199264,"uid":102722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T05:27:11.000Z","msg":"畢業兩年浮浮沈沈 人工又唔見會加<br />\n有無好介紹<br />\n利申：三大"},{"pid":"c09318a832cf91c5be50311ce0f9c0d0a006e5e1","tid":199264,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T05:35:14.000Z","msg":"銀行金融機構瘋搶IT人 行內出現『一年加一萬』的現象<br />\n<br />\n業界急須革新，缺人卻是一大難題。梁建文指出，銀行界招聘IT人特別困難，因既要熟悉IT，亦須了解銀行操作，故很難從其他行業物色，唯有在行內爭聘，以致挖角普遍，人工攀升。「行內甚至出現『一年一萬』的現象，入行做5年便有5萬元，可見缺人情況十分嚴重。」"},{"pid":"6e42547e7d180bf17b5cc09747a6beddbac9a20b","tid":199264,"uid":90390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T05:41:51.000Z","msg":"三大做兩年IT，人工起碼加10K啦，點算無咩點加。"},{"pid":"3cbc72b8018ddf7582e50e98281486e8ef4a9d73","tid":199264,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:22:46.000Z","msg":"幾錢先,<br />\n<br />\n就黎做夠2年, 得19k"},{"pid":"39d865d259080a67dc39714acb659a338e4ebc11","tid":199264,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T11:24:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢先,<br />\n<br />\n就黎做夠2年, 得19k</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b9aebcdd3cc44f72421ea00e6a86b56eeb9e15","tid":199264,"uid":102722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢先,<br />\n<br />\n就黎做夠2年, 得19k</blockquote><br />\n同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e016da1f51a1ac3a227fa745b35aa6dcee1c03","tid":199264,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08